Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.43,0:00:05.48,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Senpai?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:09.48,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She doesn't stay late enough \Nto eat dinner in the office often...}Hiếm khi thấy chị ấy tăng ca ở lại quá giờ ăn tối.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:12.14,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{March on, Meowtaro!}Tiến lên Nyantaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.14,0:00:16.06,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Meow, meow, meow! Meow, meow, meow!}nya nya nya! Nya nya nya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:15.32,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She's singing her heart out!}Chị ấy đang hát kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.67,0:00:17.58,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She noticed me?}Phát hiện ra rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:22.42,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{March on, Meowtaro!}Tiến lên Nyantaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:23.05,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She kept singing?!}Vẫn đang hát?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.42,0:00:24.37,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Meow, meow, meow!}Nya nya nya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.78,0:00:27.00,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And she wants me to join in?!}Và muốn mình hát chung?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:29.00,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Meow, meow, meow!}Nya, nya, nya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:32.51,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Good job, Shinozaki-san! \NThat was nicely done.}Em làm tốt lắm Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:36.06,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What a cute abuse of authority.}Lạm quyền mà dễ thương quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:44.12,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{Oh, I love you so much, I just have to laugh}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:53.74,Show_Title,Title sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H292A2F&\bord0}{My }{\1a&HFF&\bord1\3c&HA183CA&}{T}{\3c&H000000&}{iny }{\bord0\1a&H00&}{Senpai}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:56.82,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{We've got an emergency here}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:59.60,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{Are you paying attention, me?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:05.83,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{There's someone other than me \Ndancing around inside of my heart}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:08.08,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{I want to talk to her}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:11.13,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{I want to touch her}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:16.62,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{Look, I get it, but for now try to pipe down}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.13,0:01:19.84,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{What in the world am I doing?}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:22.60,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{You're right next to me}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:28.85,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{And this is the perfect chance...}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:30.43,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{HONEY}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.43,0:01:35.14,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{I'm trapped by that sweet rich taste}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.14,0:01:38.35,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{And I don't think I can ever escape}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.35,0:01:40.85,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{I may as well just sink into it}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:41.68,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{HONEY}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.68,0:01:46.45,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{It's another day in your dazzling presence}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:49.46,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{We may never be \Non the same page with this love but}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:55.89,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{Oh, I love you so much, I just have to laugh}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:13.09,Main - Top,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{\an8}{What should I drink?}Uống gì đây nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:17.99,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{Working late on your entry? Good for you.}Tăng ca đêm à? Đỉnh ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:20.48,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{Here, for you.}Đây, tặng cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:22.12,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Thank... you...}Cảm... ơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:25.62,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{Why not just throw together something simple?}Sao không kết hợp mấy thứ đơn giản lại cho dễ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:29.70,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{Well, I'm headed home. See you around!}Tôi về đây. Chào nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:34.26,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Can't just... throw something together.}Sao mà... được chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.74,0:02:36.53,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Need to help the director aim higher...}Phải nhắm đến vị trí cao hơn vì nhóm trưởng.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.96,0:02:40.97,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Good morning.}Chào buổi sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:44.89,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What's wrong, everyone?}Sao thế mọi người?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:47.14,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I should be the one asking you that!}Chị phải hỏi em mới đúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.44,0:02:51.15,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The deadline for the competition \Nis soon. He might be overdoing it...}Hạn chót sắp đến rồi. Có vẻ em ấy đang cố quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:54.25,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, I'm totally fine!}Em vẫn ổn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:56.17,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is what I say but...}Nói là thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:59.86,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm freaking out on the inside!}Mình đang sắp thăng rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:03.62,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The pressure of competing directly \Nwith someone at work for the first time,}Áp lực của cuộc thi khi tham gia lần đầu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:06.99,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{the responsibility of needing \Nto keep our manager with us...}Trách nhiệm bảo vệ quản lý.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:13.13,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's so much I could use some rehab, \Nbut I can't tell Senpai that!}Quá nhiều thứ phải lo khiến mình bú nước \Ntăng lực liên tục, không thể nói cho chị ấy biết!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:16.80,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{See...? I'm fine... \NNow, let's get to work...}Em vẫn ổn mà... vào làm thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:21.93,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san.}Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.66,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Specially made by your senpai, \Nit's the kanji for "person."}Đồ đặc biệt từ đàn chị nè. Chữ Nhân đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:28.52,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Please, eat up.}Ăn đi em.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:32.36,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Wh-Why?}T-Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:35.98,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You're worried about your proposal for \Nthe competition being perfect, aren't you?}Em đang lo lắng về \Nviệc phát biểu trước nhiều người nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:41.07,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Please don't be afraid to fail. \NIt doesn't matter if it goes smoothly.}Đừng sợ thất bại. Nếu không suôn sẻ cũng chẳng sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:44.57,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'd even say this contest is about \Naccepting that kind of thing.}Cuộc thi này không có ý nghĩa như thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:47.34,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Just swing as hard as you can!}Cứ thoải mái và hết mình là được.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.34,0:03:49.45,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{And it's just accepted I'll miss?}Vậy không thắng cũng được ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:51.46,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:51.96,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Yep!}Ừm.
