Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.21,Sign_Basic,Office Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(454,212)\an9\c&H2C3437&\bord0\shad0\b1\fs20}{Group 1}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.21,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{Magnificent!}Tuyệt vời!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:58.48,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{The concept, the targeting... \NBoth are clearly laid out and easy to grasp.}Khái niệm, mục tiêu... tất cả đều rõ ràng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:03:59.97,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:03.73,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{All you need now is an image to \Nillustrate the complete project}Giờ chỉ cần hình ảnh minh hoạ là đủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:03.22,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H1A1C1C&\pos(156.667,108)\an8\frz13.25\bord0\shad0\b1}{The Ultimate Meowtaro}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.73,0:04:06.18,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{and it'll be an even easier sell.}Và nó sẽ dễ dàng được bán ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.74,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{An illustration...}Hình ảnh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:10.72,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{Yeah. Even a simple one would be fine.}Ừm, đơn giản thôi cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:16.11,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{You're almost there. \NDon't worry, Kurusu. You can do this!}Em sắp đạt được rồi. Nếu là em thì sẽ được.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:19.51,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Right...}Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:26.78,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai helped me calm down some.}Chị ấy đã giúp mình bình tĩnh lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:29.29,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Okay, let's do this...}Rồi, cố lên thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.08,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, sorry!}Xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.76,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Chị nè...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:51.54,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You know that girl, Kurusu, \Nin Development Group 1?}Chị biết nhóm phát triển số 1 \Ncó người tên Kurusu không?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.52,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Sure, I do.}Biết chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:56.82,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{She's taking on the new hire contest like me,}Cậu ta cũng tham gia giải tân binh cùng em.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:05:00.66,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{and I think she's feeling \Njust as much pressure.}Và em nghĩ cậu ấy đang gặp áp lực.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:06.16,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{If you see her, I'd appreciate it if you \Ncould try and help her feel better...}Nếu chị có gặp thì xin chị \Nhãy giúp cậu ấy bình tĩnh lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:11.33,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Sorry, I know I shouldn't be \Nasking you to do this!}Xin lỗi, em biết không nên nhờ việc này...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:14.00,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{But I think she'd be too on-guard around me.}Nhưng do cậu ta đề phòng em quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:18.00,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Cơ mà có vẻ em thích xen vào chuyện người khác rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:21.25,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Understood.}Chị biết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:23.93,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'll keep that in mind.}Chị sẽ để ý.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:25.26,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I appreciate it.}Vâng ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:34.56,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Still working?}Vẫn đang làm việc à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:40.52,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{You're from Development Group 2...}Chị bên nhóm 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.45,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Chị là Katase Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:45.03,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Do you always stay this late?}Em lúc nào cũng về trễ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:47.85,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{That's none of your business.}Không liên quan đến chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:51.91,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{There are some things a third party \Nmight have a clearer view on, though.}Có những thứ mà chỉ người\N không liên quan mới nhìn thấy đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:54.41,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Group 2 is the enemy.}Nhóm 2 là kẻ địch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:56.29,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{I have nothing to say to you.}Em không có gì nói cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:58.25,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Do you mind if I sit with you?}Thế chị ngồi đây nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:05:59.43,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Listen to me!}Chị có nghe không!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.04,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That pouch...}Cái túi đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:05.80,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It was released for Meowtaro's \N20th anniversary, wasn't it?}Hàng kỉ niệm 20 năm Nyantaro nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.93,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{You recognize it?!}Chị nhận ra sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:10.11,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I have one, too.}Chị cũng có mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:13.53,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{There was another one \Nthat came out with a ribbon...}Còn một bé có đeo nơ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:16.14,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{I have that one, too!}Em cũng có.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:20.37,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Meowtaro's head was rounder \Nback then, with smaller eyes,}Nyantaro mặt tròn mắt nhỏ,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:23.54,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{and you could tell the art was more \Nanalog, but that made it cuter...}tuy hình ảnh phong cách cũ nhưng nó dễ thương...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.94,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{A-And well...}V-Và...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:32.45,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Even though this is the Meowtaro company... \NI don't get many chances to talk about him...}Dù là công ty tạo nên Nyantaro \Nnhưng em không có ai để nói về sở thích...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:37.21,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Please, have a seat.}Chị... có thể ngồi cạnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:38.96,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn em.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:42.74,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{If you like Meowtaro that much,}Nếu em thích nyantaro đến thế,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:45.50,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{you must be really motivated \Nfor the rookie competition, too.}hẳn phải rất quyết tâm trong cuộc thi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:51.35,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Katase-san...}Chị Katase...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:57.72,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Katase-san, is there anything \Nyou have trouble with at work?}Chị có từng gặp rắc rối trong công việc không?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:03.19,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{A whole lot of things!}Nhiều lắm chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:06.32,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Laying out diagrams and adjusting text...}Bố trí sơ đồ nè, điều chỉnh văn bản nè...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.31,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Could you look at this?}Chị có thể xem qua nó không?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:18.88,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Does it remind you of any Taro in particular?}Chị có nghĩ đây là Nyantaro không?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.88,0:07:21.08,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That's a very leading question!}Câu hỏi có tính dẫn dắt quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:24.84,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{I'm no good at art...}Em không giỏi vẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:27.53,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{I've managed to keep that \Na secret the past year.}Em đã giấu nó trong suốt nhiều năm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:30.29,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{But I can't anymore...}Nhưng giờ không thể nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:35.72,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{I don't want to disappoint her.}Em không muốn làm chị ấy thất vọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:39.46,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{I've tried so many times...}Em đã thử rất nhiều...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:41.23,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{but I just can't get better.}nhưng vẫn không giỏi lên được.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:47.11,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{I want to do a good job, Katase-san!}Em muốn cố gắng, chị Katase!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:50.11,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{How can I deliver for her?}Phải làm sao để đáp lại chị ấy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:52.61,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{What do I do?}Em phải làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:55.62,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Maybe you should just...}Em chỉ cần...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:58.37,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{tell her that you can't do it.}nói là mình không làm được.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:01.92,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{But if I do that...}Nhưng nếu nói vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:05.10,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Admitting when you can't do \Nsomething is part of your job.}Có những việc mình không thể làm được chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.14,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Besides...}Với cả...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:15.27,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{No one's going to ridicule you\Nfor having tried your best.}không ai chế nhạo những người cố gắng hết sức cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:22.22,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Okay... I'll try and tell her.}Vâng... em sẽ nói với chị ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.11,0:08:25.99,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Director.}Trưởng phòng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:30.49,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{I've... updated my proposal.}Em... đã sửa lại kế hoạch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:32.90,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Please, look...}Hãy xem qua...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:37.81,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{Sure. Knowing you, Kurusu, \NI'm sure it's evolved a fair...}Được thôi. Quả không hổ là Kurusu. \NEm giải quyết nhanh gọn...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:44.16,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H1A1C1C&\pos(156.667,108)\an8\frz13.25\bord0\shad0\b1}{The Ultimate Meowtaro}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:41.74,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{This art...}Bức vẽ này...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:43.75,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{I'm... so sorry.}Em... xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:49.66,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{I tried, but... it was... \Nthe best I could do...}Em đã thử... nhưng đây là bức tốt nhất...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:57.18,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{You said I would be able \Nto do it... but I failed!}Em... không thể làm được... khiến chị thất vọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:02.93,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{No, you didn't...}Không có gì thất vọng cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:05.19,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{You didn't fail, Kurusu.}Em không làm chị thất vọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:07.37,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{I should be the one to apologize.}Chị mới là người phải xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:11.44,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{I thought I was encouraging you, \Nbut I was just pouring on more pressure.}Chị cứ nghĩ mình phải cổ vũ em, \Nnhưng cuối cùng lại đặt áp lực lên em.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.77,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{Please, forgive me, Kurusu.}Tha thứ cho chị, Kurusu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:15.69,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Director...}Trưởng phòng...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:21.05,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{Hanaoka-san, could you help \Nwith Kurusu's proposal?}Hanaoka, em giúp Kurusu được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:22.20,Main,Hanaoka,0,0,0,,{Sure.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.53,0:09:23.65,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Sorry about this...}Em xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:25.21,Main,Hanaoka,0,0,0,,{It's no problem at all.}Không sao cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:28.36,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{There's a couple of days left \Nbefore the deadline!}Còn vài ngày nữa là đến hạn chót.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:31.46,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{We're going to support Kurusu \Nas much as we can in that time!}Chúng ta sẽ hỗ trợ Kurusu hết mình!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:33.46,Main,Dev Group 1,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:37.10,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Development Group 1 is really motivated.}Nhóm 1 có vẻ đang hào hứng nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:37.72,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.05,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What a relief...}May quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:50.98,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{He's under a lot of pressure himself, but he's \Nstill nice enough to worry about others...}Em ấy cũng đang rất áp lực\N nhưng vẫn quan tâm đến người khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:58.13,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Did I do something funny?}Em làm gì khiến chị cười hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:01.55,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Not at all. I'm just impressed \Nwith you, Shinozaki-san.}Không có gì. Không hổ danh là em.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:05.11,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Wh-What for, Senpai?}L-Là sao ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.37,Main,Shiori+Kurusu,0,0,0,,{March on, Meowtaro!}Tiến lên Nyantaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:09.98,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Meow, meow, meow!}Nya, nya, nya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:12.00,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Meow, meow, meow!}Nya, nya, nya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:16.29,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{\i1}{My Tiny Meowtaro}{\i0}{.}Câu chuyện về bé Nyantaro dễ thương của tôi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:17.58,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{You sure that's the title?}Ủa? Nhầm tựa phim à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:20.89,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's finally the day of the competition.}Cuối cùng cũng đến ngày diễn ra cuộc thi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.64,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Everything ready, Shinozaki-san?}Mọi thứ ổn chứ Shinozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:25.64,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yep! All set.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:28.14,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You're absolutely sure you're ready?}Em chắc chắn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:30.40,Main,Shinozakui,0,0,0,,{I am really sure that I'm all set!}Em chắc chắn mọi thứ luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:33.90,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I have to say...}Cơ mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:36.90,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I didn't expect you to make \Na Meowtaro costume...}Không ngờ em làm nguyên bộ Nyantaro đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:39.22,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Are you a goddess, Hayakawa-san?!}Hayakawa là thánh thần à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:40.93,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Not really, no.}Không hẳn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:45.07,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Compared to my usual, cosplay it was \Npretty simple, so it's not like...}So với mấy đồ cosplay em\N hay làm thì cái này đơn giản...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:45.07,Main - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Your usual what?}Hay làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:48.70,Main,Hayakwa,0,0,0,,{Uh, er, nothing! Never mind!}Không có gì đâu ạ!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.04,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{Oh, my.}Chà chà.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:54.22,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Thank you for all your help, Senpai.}Cảm ơn vì đã giúp em.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:55.33,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's all right.}Không không.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:11:00.35,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai, is it just me, or are you \Nmore nervous than I am?}Chị... đang lo lắng hơn cả em à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:03.94,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{My direct subordinate is entering his \Nbiggest moment of the entire year!}Đàn em của chị đang bước vào võ đài lớn nhất mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:06.43,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Of course I am!}Chị phải lo chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:09.43,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I am so full of butterflies right now...}Đầu chị đang bay bổng lắm nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:12.88,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai, calm down. It'll be okay.}Bình tĩnh nào chị, em sẽ ổn thôi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:12.88,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Is there anything else I can do?}Có chuyện gì chị có thể làm không?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:16.10,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Kurusu-san.}Kurusu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:22.32,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{During the presentations... I go on before you.}Hôm nay tôi ... sẽ phát biểu trước cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:26.20,Main,SFX Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(116,195)\c&HA0A5B0&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs14\bord1.5\4c&H907C86&}{Hrmmm}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:26.20,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It kind of ended up feeling like \Na showdown, didn't it?}Tự nhiên cảm giác thành cuộc đấu của hai người luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:28.97,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Let's both do our best.}Hãy cùng cố hết sức nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:29.81,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Um...}Này...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:32.17,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:38.80,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Katase-san mentioned... \Nyou were worried about me.}Chị Katase đã nói... cậu lo lắng cho tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:44.93,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{I'm... grateful.}Cảm ơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:47.68,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Sure.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:49.21,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:54.81,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{We're going to win. \NWin, and take your manager.}Bọn tôi sẽ thắng và cướp lấy quản lý bên cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:58.02,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I don't intend on losing, either.}Tôi cũng không định thua đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:12:00.57,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{We're going to win, and keep our manager!}Bọn tôi sẽ thắng và không giao anh ấy cho ai cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:07.02,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Looking forward to your presentation.}Tôi mong chờ lắm đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:11.30,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Okay! Let's do this!}Rồi! Cố lên nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:15.98,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{This talk about losing \Nor keeping the manager...}Nếu thua sẽ bị cướp mất quản lý?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:18.12,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What's that all about?}Chuyện này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:22.42,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Uh, well... the truth is...}À... sự thật là...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:24.55,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{The truth is...?}Là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:28.93,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Excuse me?!}Cái gì cơ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:34.49,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Report! Stay in contact! Consult!}Báo cáo! Liên lạc! Bàn bạc!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:38.19,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(316,72)\an8\fs16\b1\bord0\shad0\c&H000000&}{Report}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:38.19,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(316,132)\an8\fs16\b1\bord0\shad0\c&H000000&}{Stay in contact}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:38.19,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(316,192)\an8\fs16\b1\bord0\shad0\c&H000000&}{Consult}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:36.88,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You didn't do any one of those!}Em không làm một điều nào luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:38.19,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Sorry...}Xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:40.30,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{I knew about it.}Anh biết mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:41.12,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Me, too.}Em cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:43.11,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{So I'm the only one who didn't?!}Vậy chỉ mình em là không biết sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:46.58,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Maybe we can still negotiate...}Nếu là giờ thì vẫn còn thời gian...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:50.28,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{But she's probably already into her proposal...}Nhưng giờ em ấy đã lên phát biểu rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:52.25,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What do we do?!}Phải làm sao đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:53.75,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai.}Chị à.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:58.13,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Specially made by your kouhai, \Nit's the kanji for "person."}Chữ Nhân làm bởi đàn em nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:03.26,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I really am sorry that \NI didn't tell you sooner.}Em xin lỗi vì không nói gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:08.26,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{But I've been under your guidance \Nfor a whole year now.}Nhưng em đã được chị dẫn dắt suốt 1 năm qua.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:13.77,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I know I won't lose.}Nên em sẽ không thua đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:21.58,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Gosh... if you put it like that...}Thiệt tình... nếu em nói thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:25.28,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I won't be able to say anything back.}Thì chị không có gì để nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:32.04,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san is guaranteed to win \Nthe most valuable rookie award!}Shinozaki nhất định sẽ chiến thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:32.78,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Right!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:35.79,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Giờ chỉ cần lên tinh thần là đủ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:36.90,Main,Shinozaki/Manager,0,0,0,,{Okay!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:36.90,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Okay...}Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:39.42,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Development Group 2, fight!}Nhóm phát triển số 2, fight!
