Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:35.48,Main,President,0,0,0,,{Out of all the submissions, the one selected \Nfor the most prestigious prize is...}Bài dự thi giành được giải thưởng danh giá nhất...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:38.48,Main,President,0,0,0,,{Yamagishi's team from Public Relations!}Nhóm quan hệ công chúng của Yamagishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:42.19,Main,Yamagishi (M),0,0,0,,{No way... Me?}Đùa à... mình á?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:44.12,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{Yay!}Yê!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:46.44,Main,MC,0,0,0,,{Where did you get the idea \Nfor your proposal from?}Cậu lấy ý tưởng lần này ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:48.22,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Nowhere in particular...}Không có gì đặc biệt...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:51.09,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{It's all thanks to my daily guidance!}Là nhờ tôi đã chỉ dẫn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:54.04,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{He was the least motivated, and yet...!}Là người ít động lực nhất vậy mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:57.00,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{This is... really frustrating.}Cay thế nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:20:01.93,Main,MC,0,0,0,,{And that concludes the annual \Nnew hire competition.}Và cuộc thi tân binh lần này xin phép được khép lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:06.00,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san, you did a great job!}Shinozaki, em vất vả rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:08.65,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{There's a big wrap party to celebrate, too.}Tổ chức tiệc thôi nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:10.93,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{It'll be my victory party!}Tiệc chiến thắng của anh nhỉ!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:11.92,Main,Yamagishi; shinozaki; Kurusu,0,0,0,,{No, it won't be.}Không không không.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:13.02,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{Right?!}Nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:30.23,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{Bleary-eyed and not fully awake from a dream}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:35.13,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{I still can't bring myself \Nto drink that bitter coffee}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:39.61,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{So I sneakily toss in \Ntwo pinches of a sweet secret}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:43.83,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{And let it slowly spread throughout}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:48.79,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{There's a local bakery \Nthat's only open sometimes}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:53.68,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{Where I once had some toast that glittered}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:58.18,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{What is it that makes it so satisfying?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:21:02.35,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{Almost like magic}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:07.43,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{I find myself thinking about that kind of thing}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:13.04,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{How the small things can be the most precious}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:17.83,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{Deep inside my heart}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:22.23,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{It's ever so bittersweet}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:27.15,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{"Just being around you is enough"}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.15,0:21:31.17,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{Becomes my mantra}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.17,0:21:33.46,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{Baby like sugar}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:42.72,Main,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{Baby you're the sugar}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.31,0:21:48.29,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Work drags so much in the afternoon...}Làm việc buổi chiều mệt mỏi ghê...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.29,0:21:49.56,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Uh-huh, uh-huh.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:51.45,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Just the excellence one.}Chỉ là xuất sắc nhất thôi hè.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:55.01,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{It ain't like that at all!}Nó hỏng có giống thế đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:00.21,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,Ngắt máy nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:04.34,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Forget... what you heard.}Quên... những gì cậu nghe đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:06.09,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Not gonna happen that fast.}Tự nhiên bảo thế sao quên ngay được.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:08.72,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Don't try the physical approach.}Đừng có làm thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.82,0:22:11.93,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{What's the big deal anyway?}Có gì mà không thích?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:14.49,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{It's... embarrassing.}Vì nó xấu hổ...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:16.73,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{I don't see how.}Có gì mà xấu hổ.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:22.75,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{We don't have any sort of obvious accent \Nwhere I'm from, so I'm kinda jealous.}Bọn này còn không có giọng \Nđịa phương để nói đây, ghen tị ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.27,0:22:25.99,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Jealous...?}Ghen tị?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:27.99,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Yeah, it's kinda cool.}Ngầu mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:33.12,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Man, lunch is gonna end \Nif we don't wrap up here.}Cứ đứng đó sẽ hết giờ nghỉ trưa đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:34.74,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{H-Hey...}N-Này...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.61,0:22:39.25,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Thank you kindly.}Cảm ơn vì lòng tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:43.77,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Thank me whatly?}Cảm ơn vì cái gì?
